CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe Minister for Defence had to
OL,7,Fabandon a trip to Lebanon on security
OL,8,Fadvice from the Defence Forces.
OL,10,FHelen McEntee had been due to meet
OL,11,FIrish peacekeepers deployed as part of
OL,12,Fthe United Nations Interim Force in
OL,13,FLebanon (Unifil) but the visit was
OL,14,Fcalled off following the military's
OL,15,Foperational advice that it was "not
OL,16,Ftenable".
OL,26,@wD@`OUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FIn its latest update, the Defence
OL,7,FForces said all personnel in Lebanon
OL,8,Fare "well and accounted for" amid
OL,9,Fheightened clashes between the Israeli
OL,10,Fmilitary and Hezbollah.
OL,12,FIt comes after a Polish member of
OL,13,FIreland's joint battalion with Poland
OL,14,Fsustained minor injuries from a
OL,15,F"roadside device", while three
OL,16,FIndonesian peacekeepers were killed in
OL,17,Fother blasts.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@\O]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Chief of Staff Lieutenant
OL,7,FGeneral Rossa Mulcahy said: "I can
OL,8,Fconfirm that all our personnel across
OL,9,Fthese three UN missions in the Middle
OL,10,FEast, are well and accounted for; amid
OL,11,Fongoing tensions in the region.
OL,13,F"Any developments that may affect
OL,14,Ftheir safety are monitored in real
OL,15,Ftime and appropriate actions are
OL,16,Ftaken."
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FMs McEntee said: "I will continue to
OL,7,Fwork closely with partners to enhance
OL,8,Fforce protection, contingency planning
OL,9,Fand ensure the mission can operate
OL,10,Feffectively in an increasingly
OL,11,Fvolatile environment.
OL,13,F"Ireland remains steadfast in its
OL,14,Fcommitment to peacekeeping and to
OL,15,Fsupporting stability in Lebanon."
OL,26,@nD@ROUuD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
