OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe cancellation of Ms McEntee's trip
OL,7,Fpresented an opportunity the Defence
OL,8,FForces was able to exploit to pull off
OL,9,Fits first personnel rotation in a
OL,10,Fconflict zone using new "strategic
OL,11,Freach" capability.
OL,13,FLast Friday, the Defence Forces
OL,14,Fconfirmed it carried out an operation
OL,15,Fto transport key battalion personnel
OL,16,Fto UN Post 2-45 in Lebanon, known as
OL,17,FCamp Shamrock, and to return
OL,18,Fcommunications specialists who had
OL,19,Fbeen performing critical maintenance
OL,20,Fto communication systems and
OL,21,Finfrastructure.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe mission involved a young female
OL,7,FAir Corps pilot flying the plane into
OL,8,Fthe "volatile region" to rendezvous
OL,9,Fwith Army personnel who conducted an
OL,10,Farmoured patrol from UNP 2-45 to
OL,11,FBeirut Airport for the personnel and
OL,12,Fequipment handover.
OL,14,FIt was the first such operation using
OL,15,Fthe strategic reach capability of the
OL,16,FAir Corps, following the delivery of a
OL,17,FC295 transport aircraft last year.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe Defence Forces said it needed to
OL,7,Fconduct the mission because a civilian
OL,8,Fair partner had cancelled a planned
OL,9,Fflight to rotate personnel in and out,
OL,10,Fover concerns of the increased risk in
OL,11,FBeirut's airspace.
OL,13,FThis left key personnel, including
OL,14,Fmedical battalion headquarters staff
OL,15,Fand medics, unable to return to the
OL,16,Fbattalion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FAt the same time, several
OL,7,Fcommunication specialists deployed to
OL,8,Fwork on systems across Unifil's area
OL,9,Fof operations were also due to leave
OL,10,Fon a cancelled flight.
OL,12,FThe Defence Forces uses a range of
OL,13,Fapproaches to rotate personnel in and
OL,14,Fout of overseas bases like Lebanon,
OL,15,Fincluding commercial aircraft and
OL,16,Fchartered flights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FUsing its own planes or chartering
OL,7,Fflights is a complicated process which
OL,8,Fcan take weeks to secure the necessary
OL,9,Fairport slots and diplomatic
OL,10,Fclearances in collaboration with the
OL,11,FDepartment of Defence and Department
OL,12,Fof Foreign Affairs.
OL,14,FAs the Minister's trip got cancelled,
OL,15,Fthe Defence Forces were still able to
OL,16,Fuse slots and clearances it had
OL,17,Falready obtained to conduct a
OL,18,Fdifferent flight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FOver the course of five-to-six days,
OL,7,Foperations personnel analysed the
OL,8,Frisks, secured departmental sign-off,
OL,9,Fand conducted the new flight.
OL,11,FThe operation was a success thanks to
OL,12,Fthe increased capability provided to
OL,13,Fthe Air Corps by the C295 aircraft,
OL,14,Faccording to the director of
OL,15,Foperations and plans at Defence Forces
OL,16,Fheadquarters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FColonel Denis Hanly said it was a
OL,7,F"force multiplier", adding that the
OL,8,Fmission was proof of increased
OL,9,Fflexibility for the operations team,
OL,10,Fwith the C295 also due to be used for
OL,11,Fpersonnel in Kosovo.
OL,13,F"We proved the concept ` and we can do
OL,14,Fit again," he said.
OL,16,FThe Lebanon mission required ongoing
OL,17,Frisk analysis and mitigation,
OL,18,Ftechnical overwatch from multiple
OL,19,Fsources, and cooperation between many
OL,20,Fteams including the Irish Military
OL,21,FIntelligence Service.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]uD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FCol Hanley said securing sign off from
OL,7,FGovernment departments was swift: "The
OL,8,Fdoors we pushed opened very easily."
OL,10,FTwenty-six personnel flew into the
OL,11,Fcountry with around 600kgs of
OL,12,Fequipment and supplies for deployed
OL,13,Ftroops, while 17 travelled back.
OL,15,FThe overall numbers include two pilots
OL,16,Fand air crew, as well as a medic who
OL,17,Ftravelled on each leg.
OL,19,FThey extracted the communications
OL,20,F"work party", swapped chaplains, and
OL,21,Fcarried out a medical repatriation.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@dO]|D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe rotation was carried out while
OL,7,F"ongoing combat operations" were still
OL,8,Fhappening in south Lebanon, with
OL,9,Fstrikes around Beirut visible the
OL,10,Fnight before landing at the airport.
OL,12,FTroops from Camp Shamrock travelled in
OL,13,Fa heavily armoured convoy of Mowag
OL,14,Fpersonnel carriers to Beirut Airport
OL,15,Fin order to be there before the plane
OL,16,Flanded.
OL,18,FCol Hanly said: "We wanted a Ryanair
OL,19,Fturnover ` as quickly as possible, no
OL,20,Fhugs or high fives."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]zD@QOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FThe handover, which involved unloading
OL,7,Fthe equipment and supplies before
OL,8,Ftaking off again, took 30 minutes `
OL,9,Fand the operations director said it
OL,10,Fcould be done faster.
OL,12,FThe convoy took close to four hours to
OL,13,Freturn to Camp Shamrock, which is
OL,14,Falmost double what it would normally
OL,15,Ftake because of the increased risk in
OL,16,Fthe region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FCol Hanly, who gained specific
OL,7,Fexperience around force protection of
OL,8,Faircraft and airfields in Afghanistan,
OL,9,Fsaid there was a "calm confidence"
OL,10,Fthroughout the operation.
OL,12,FHe said it has allowed the Defence
OL,13,FForces to refresh leadership and key
OL,14,Fcapability personnel as well as bring
OL,15,Fvehicles used by Unifil peacekeepers
OL,16,Fback into service.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FMany of the personnel who were brought
OL,7,Fover were not present for the first
OL,8,Fweeks of the heightened conflict and
OL,9,Fare now returning to "austere field
OL,10,Fconditions".
OL,12,FCol Hanly paid tribute to the courage
OL,13,Fand strength of those deployed in
OL,14,FLebanon, adding that he did not
OL,15,Fcurrently have concerns for the
OL,16,Foverall supplies at the camp ` but
OL,17,Freferenced measures like 30-second
OL,18,Fshowers and food preservation as
OL,19,Frestrictions that can be used in times
OL,20,Fof shortage.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FHe said there are "significant clashes
OL,7,Facross the entire area of operations"
OL,8,Ffor the Irish personnel, with
OL,9,F"significant formations" operating in
OL,10,Fthe region.
OL,12,FOf ongoing concern is Israeli strikes
OL,13,Fon bridges over the Litani River,
OL,14,Flimiting access to Unifil's area of
OL,15,Foperations.
OL,17,FHe said there had been no evidence of
OL,18,FUnifil being specifically targeted in
OL,19,Fthe Irish area of operations but added
OL,20,Fthat events need to be fully
OL,21,Finvestigated.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@eO]qD@AOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FDespite last week's operation, a
OL,7,Fnumber of the personnel who had been
OL,8,Fdue to return on leave were unable to
OL,9,Fdo so because of the changing flight
OL,10,Fplans but remain on stand-by to return.
OL,12,FCol Hanly said the latest figures show
OL,13,Fthere are 1.3 million people displaced
OL,14,Fin Lebanon, including 300,000 children
OL,15,F` with 1,300 fatalities and 4,000
OL,16,Finjuries.
OL,18,FWith the next rotation due in May, Col
OL,19,FHanly said the Defence Forces is not
OL,20,Fresting "on its laurels".
OL,26,@|D@IOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FHe said he had spoken to the new
OL,7,Fbattalion leader and that planning for
OL,8,Fthe next rotation is "at an advanced
OL,9,Fstage".
OL,11,FOn a longer term, The Defence Forces
OL,12,Fis actively planning for the
OL,13,Fconclusion of the Unifil mission and
OL,14,Fwithdrawal from Lebanon.
OL,16,FThe UN Security Council mandate for
OL,17,Fthe mission expires on December 31,
OL,18,Ffollowed by a 12-month drawdown and
OL,19,Fultimate liquidation.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30420
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775178189
OL,3,CMinister's trip to Lebanon cancelled
OL,4,Cfollowing Defence Forces concern
OL,6,FAfter May, there will also be a
OL,7,Frotation of Irish personnel in
OL,8,FNovember ` which is expected to have a
OL,9,Flarger logistical footprint to deal
OL,10,Fwith the end of the mission.
OL,12,FThere will still be a requirement for
OL,13,Fa "heavy security footprint", but the
OL,14,Fpersonnel will likely be dealing with
OL,15,Fmultiple convoys carrying Irish
OL,16,Fequipment as well as force protection
OL,17,Fas the installations are collapsed.
OL,26,@uD@COUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
